{"tid":1948842,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"汽車保險墊底問題","createTime":"2020-03-29T09:12:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T02:32:19.000Z","uid":80292,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d3ce418c84681c8f03f954dbe81022a056bcb8b2","tid":1948842,"uid":80292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T09:12:58.000Z","msg":"之前意外涉及政府車，報左保險，上庭認左老不。<br />\n宜家政府claim我$2000，我份保險墊底$5000。<br />\n想問：<br />\n1. 唔交比保險處理，自己比左佢有無問題？<br />\n2. 如1）可行，是否代表無claim過同唔影響NCB?"},{"pid":"8fdf2b7fea26c518c32559ddd459a6b56a62d705","tid":1948842,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T09:21:30.000Z","msg":"其實你應該喺上庭前報保險<br />\n衰啲講句, 就算政府而家claim你二十萬, 你想報保險都冇得報<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ebaf32939ebbef4c8c593f613a89ef64fa1c48","tid":1948842,"uid":9230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T09:29:01.000Z","msg":"應該咁講，你交俾保險保險都係叫你食自己，因為below 底<br />\n<br />\n因為below 底，佢唔可以扣你NCD,但你有意外同扣分紀錄都係下年續保嘅因素"},{"pid":"f0fa076ea96fbcbe2c54ed1210a7008fcc9246d0","tid":1948842,"uid":80292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fdf2b7fea26c518c32559ddd459a6b56a62d705","tid":1948842,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T09:21:30.000Z","msg":"其實你應該喺上庭前報保險<br />\n衰啲講句, 就算政府而家claim你二十萬, 你想報保險都冇得報<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:23:52.000Z","msg":"我幾時話我上庭前無報保險？"},{"pid":"32dd6b29a355d05196f08d817acee2d558168f32","tid":1948842,"uid":80292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78ebaf32939ebbef4c8c593f613a89ef64fa1c48","tid":1948842,"uid":9230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T09:29:01.000Z","msg":"應該咁講，你交俾保險保險都係叫你食自己，因為below 底<br />\n<br />\n因為below 底，佢唔可以扣你NCD,但你有意外同扣分紀錄都係下年續保嘅因素"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:25:29.000Z","msg":"唔該晒，即係NCB唔扣，但可能會因為意外同扣分加我保費同loading?"},{"pid":"d7959e8e4e50a314d1e4498473e9662406dfe9ad","tid":1948842,"uid":198035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:27:11.000Z","msg":"NCD即係no claim discount，你claim得就會扣"},{"pid":"beea30d4e1a871519732a94ab29a4cc6e95e11db","tid":1948842,"uid":198035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7959e8e4e50a314d1e4498473e9662406dfe9ad","tid":1948842,"uid":198035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:27:11.000Z","msg":"NCD即係no claim discount，你claim得就會扣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:27:42.000Z","msg":"唔claim 唔影響"},{"pid":"cbacb234c941b7220731b843ff98af36d9012912","tid":1948842,"uid":108244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:28:43.000Z","msg":"BTW 賠2000蚊真係執身彩, 街邊一個司機私了都應該唔止"},{"pid":"4671a74e69c2fa99867a745810d2f3d3f700f3d4","tid":1948842,"uid":56287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"32dd6b29a355d05196f08d817acee2d558168f32","tid":1948842,"uid":80292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78ebaf32939ebbef4c8c593f613a89ef64fa1c48","tid":1948842,"uid":9230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T09:29:01.000Z","msg":"應該咁講，你交俾保險保險都係叫你食自己，因為below 底<br />\n<br />\n因為below 底，佢唔可以扣你NCD,但你有意外同扣分紀錄都係下年續保嘅因素"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:25:29.000Z","msg":"唔該晒，即係NCB唔扣，但可能會因為意外同扣分加我保費同loading?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:31:34.000Z","msg":"其實都冇分別<br />\n因為你就算唔claim保險<br />\n你每年續保都要申報有冇扣分記錄<br />\n佢都會加你<br />\n爭在幾錢<br />\n<br />\n萬一你冇報<br />\n而下年你touchwood因另一單要claim<br />\n保險有權唔受理<br />\n因為每單索賠保險都要求你受權佢向政府攞你過往5年嘅扣分記錄<br />\n不論大唔大鑊"},{"pid":"f4918c7870d22fdeb674f7648e172d8df8d71943","tid":1948842,"uid":219635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:36:15.000Z","msg":"有朋友做保險，可以答你，你claim得保險就算唔用，你個底都花哂同會keep 3年。NCD就扣硬因為你報左保險搞claim錢但最後冇claim都計。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ece27a42464ba8d4ff7e5c1c0da19c331d95530","tid":1948842,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:37:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有朋友做保險，可以答你，你claim得保險就算唔用，你個底都花哂同會keep 3年。<span style=\"color: red;\">NCB</span>就扣硬因為你報左保險搞claim錢但最後冇claim都計。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f2ceede68aaca5f2cb73cab91d85fd65446780e","tid":1948842,"uid":80292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbacb234c941b7220731b843ff98af36d9012912","tid":1948842,"uid":108244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:28:43.000Z","msg":"BTW 賠2000蚊真係執身彩, 街邊一個司機私了都應該唔止"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:49:35.000Z","msg":"都唔知好彩唔好彩，對方架車頭少少花同車牌裂左少少，但因為政府車無得私了要罰錢兼扣分"},{"pid":"8af6b75b36253aa105322c2f4545dbe3e4c731da","tid":1948842,"uid":80292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4918c7870d22fdeb674f7648e172d8df8d71943","tid":1948842,"uid":219635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:36:15.000Z","msg":"有朋友做保險，可以答你，你claim得保險就算唔用，你個底都花哂同會keep 3年。NCD就扣硬因為你報左保險搞claim錢但最後冇claim都計。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:53:44.000Z","msg":"即係唔claim都扣Non-claim bonus?<br />\n意外後只要填過比保險都扣？<br />\n照你咁就，個底花左有record同keep 3年，下年加保費都合理。但最後因為amount細過墊底，保險叫我食自己/無claim到，都扣NCB, 好似唔太合理"},{"pid":"483e2065112959f721adda413003fa65e7d9bab2","tid":1948842,"uid":56287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ece27a42464ba8d4ff7e5c1c0da19c331d95530","tid":1948842,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:37:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有朋友做保險，可以答你，你claim得保險就算唔用，你個底都花哂同會keep 3年。<span style=\"color: red;\">NCB</span>就扣硬因為你報左保險搞claim錢但最後冇claim都計。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T13:01:05.000Z","msg":"唔使<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nNCB 同 NCD 都得"},{"pid":"e27b9f743bc08e32e970c2614700222932bbface","tid":1948842,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8af6b75b36253aa105322c2f4545dbe3e4c731da","tid":1948842,"uid":80292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4918c7870d22fdeb674f7648e172d8df8d71943","tid":1948842,"uid":219635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:36:15.000Z","msg":"有朋友做保險，可以答你，你claim得保險就算唔用，你個底都花哂同會keep 3年。NCD就扣硬因為你報左保險搞claim錢但最後冇claim都計。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:53:44.000Z","msg":"即係唔claim都扣Non-claim bonus?<br />\n意外後只要填過比保險都扣？<br />\n照你咁就，個底花左有record同keep 3年，下年加保費都合理。但最後因為amount細過墊底，保險叫我食自己/無claim到，都扣NCB, 好似唔太合理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T13:07:19.000Z","msg":"應該咁講，佢係要keep3年<br />\n<br />\n因為佢怕你有人身傷亡無/未浮出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n保險公司唔係臨賠錢果刻先喺銀行拎錢出嚟，而係有accident report 就要預留儲備金（reserve)。即係凍結咗保險公司一定嘅資金。所以就算未正式賠錢，都實際上incur 咗claim<br />\n<br />\n但到最後（3年後）即係人身傷亡time bar咗都無人claim。保險要幾hold 起咗你嘅NCD同多收嘅保費還原，具體上車主可以要求拎返之前被影響嘅policy 出嚟做endorsement。<br />\n<br />\n當然，有啲保險或者agent 唔撚想咁煩，佢另外搵方法補返數俾車主。但好多Agent 同 insurer 側側膊，你唔識/唔記得就無件事。"},{"pid":"12b808effdc8733f4fa4eb5d04c94f447c705954","tid":1948842,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8af6b75b36253aa105322c2f4545dbe3e4c731da","tid":1948842,"uid":80292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4918c7870d22fdeb674f7648e172d8df8d71943","tid":1948842,"uid":219635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:36:15.000Z","msg":"有朋友做保險，可以答你，你claim得保險就算唔用，你個底都花哂同會keep 3年。NCD就扣硬因為你報左保險搞claim錢但最後冇claim都計。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:53:44.000Z","msg":"即係唔claim都扣Non-claim bonus?<br />\n意外後只要填過比保險都扣？<br />\n照你咁就，個底花左有record同keep 3年，下年加保費都合理。但最後因為amount細過墊底，保險叫我食自己/無claim到，都扣NCB, 好似唔太合理"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T13:19:09.000Z","msg":"係，你冇claim到唔代表保險公司冇做野，由你報保險果一刻，保險公司已經當你claim，你最後冇攞到保險公司錢都計。同岩岩位師兄答你一樣，keep 3年，3年之後NCB都有返咁上下分啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係點解咁多人咁驚上法庭claim保險？香港地撞到人就一定比人㩒住搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你好彩撞到果個係政府，政府都話跟單claim報公數，唔會似私家車司機老屈，撞到的士狗仲分分鐘屈埋你醫藥費生活費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d191659524ee972e40af876b9bdca87adfb628d7","tid":1948842,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12b808effdc8733f4fa4eb5d04c94f447c705954","tid":1948842,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8af6b75b36253aa105322c2f4545dbe3e4c731da","tid":1948842,"uid":80292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4918c7870d22fdeb674f7648e172d8df8d71943","tid":1948842,"uid":219635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:36:15.000Z","msg":"有朋友做保險，可以答你，你claim得保險就算唔用，你個底都花哂同會keep 3年。NCD就扣硬因為你報左保險搞claim錢但最後冇claim都計。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:53:44.000Z","msg":"即係唔claim都扣Non-claim bonus?<br />\n意外後只要填過比保險都扣？<br />\n照你咁就，個底花左有record同keep 3年，下年加保費都合理。但最後因為amount細過墊底，保險叫我食自己/無claim到，都扣NCB, 好似唔太合理"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T13:19:09.000Z","msg":"係，你冇claim到唔代表保險公司冇做野，由你報保險果一刻，保險公司已經當你claim，你最後冇攞到保險公司錢都計。同岩岩位師兄答你一樣，keep 3年，3年之後NCB都有返咁上下分啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係點解咁多人咁驚上法庭claim保險？香港地撞到人就一定比人㩒住搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你好彩撞到果個係政府，政府都話跟單claim報公數，唔會似私家車司機老屈，撞到的士狗仲分分鐘屈埋你醫藥費生活費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T13:23:14.000Z","msg":"你計漏咗車上面個公墓完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmo